If you do not receive your card by April 10, 2021, please go to www.uscis.gov/e-request to request that we send your new card to you. If you move, go to www.uscis.gov/addresschange to give us your new mailing address.

Please follow the instructions in the notice. If you have any questions, contact the USCIS Contact Center at www.uscis.gov/contactcenter. If you move, go to www.uscis.gov/addresschange to give us your new mailing address.

title: New Card Is Being Produced
body: On March 26, 2021, we ordered your new card for Receipt Number YSC2190070996, and will mail it to the address you gave us. If you move, go to www.uscis.gov/addresschange to give us your new mailing address.
